messages.message:
hi folks, do we need some special aws setup for lambda UDFs on crafting? im trying to create a custom function field and I get
```Uncaught exception in webserver while handling request: Error
=An error occurred (AccessDeniedException) when calling the ListVersionsByFunction operation:```
i have aws_access_key_id and aws_secret_access_key set to the AWS S3DogfoodUser creds in 1PW and aws_default_region set to us-east-1.
